room_title: Escape room "Two to Tango" by Escape Space Games in Portland
room_description: You and your partner are getting ready for a good ole fashion dance class! But there’s a mystery that must be solved before the tango begins! Is this a random game being played by strangers, or is there a something deeper going on? It’ll take 60 minutes to solve this mystery. And just when you think you’re an innocent bystander... remember... it takes two to tango!
